high_descs: Turn right to exit the room and walk into the bedroom on the left to face the bed.
Pick up the bowl from the bed.
Turn left to the white sidetable on the left.
Put the bowl on the sidetable.
Turn around and exit the room and walk to the grey sofa on the right.
Pick up the bowl from the couch.
Turn around to walk into the bedroom on the left to face the sidetable on the left of the bed.
Put the bowl on the sidetable on the right of the other bowl.
anns.task_desc: Put two bowls on the SideTable.

high_descs: Walk straight and then right to exit the room, then turn left and enter the next door on the left.
Pick up the bowl from the bed.
Walk towards the corner of the room with the sidetable.
Place the bowl on the sidetable.
Exit the room the way you came in, walk straight a few feet, then turn right and go towards the large sofa.
Pick up the bowl from the couch.
Return to the sidetable in the other room.
Place the bowl on the sidetable.
anns.task_desc: Place two bowls on a side table.

high_descs: Go the the doorway and turn left at the next doorway, and go toward the bed.
Pick up the bowl from the bed.
Go toward the sidetable with the bowl.
Place the bowl on the sidetable.
Go toward the doorway and head to the sofa.
Pick up the bowl on the sofa.
Go back toward the sidetable with the other bowl.
Place the bowl beside the other bowl on the sidetable.
anns.task_desc: Place two bowls on the SideTable.
